title: Kaliopasi Uluilakepa
text: Kaliopasi Uluilakepa (born 21 January 1999) is a <a href="Fijians">Fijian</a> born <a href="New%20Zealanders">New Zealand</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who plays for the in the <a href="National%20Provincial%20Championship%20%282006%E2%80%93present%29">Bunnings NPC</a> and the <a href="Fijian%20Drua">Fijian Drua</a> in <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a>. His position is <a href="Prop%20%28rugby%20union%29">prop</a>.
